{"tid":1725172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[[[[軍紀]]]]]","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:23:45.000Z","uid":294040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a6daeb95fb2186093937ebf8be338d44eec4f1","tid":1725172,"uid":294040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\">邊個講嘢唔識尊重人、做出有損抗爭者形象嘅事，直接私了。邊個用詞侮辱，用「五毛」「XX撚」鬧人on9唔聽人意見，所有人留言屌鳩佢，叫佢講野畀啲尊重。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都係抗爭者，唔好睇到自己高高在上，就算唔同意都要對人有基本尊重。大家都有自己諗法，唔需要迫人接受你嗰套做法。討論完，繼續做你認為要做嘅事就得。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>只有嚴格軍紀先可以團結軍隊、得民心。</strong>知自己衰嘅人即刻道歉，是乎程度搵嘢懲罰自己，判自己社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊個話割！</span></span><br />\n全世界跪低求佢唔好割...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063b1b52a6770534c12266137b01f7abcee80454","tid":1725172,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31f66175e2d172e7d1ccc77bf5225fb3da86a0f","tid":1725172,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"中大入要好多鬼搞破壞 唔想輸暫時撤退be water<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e484eebad6950177352c8cdb92dca9ce15e5b0c","tid":1725172,"uid":294040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"063b1b52a6770534c12266137b01f7abcee80454","tid":1725172,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"重要咩？"},{"pid":"39bed25eeba97af94dfa399cabd364e259ddddad","tid":1725172,"uid":258598,"like"